name: Jerrol_Chupapa
content:
Jerrol Chupapa was a male Arcona who lived during the Galactic Civil War.
Jerrol Chupapa was a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
